4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a deep neural network-aided activity detection algorithm, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence. The algorithm aims to improve the accuracy of device activity detection, which is a key concern in AI. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a deep neural network-aided activity detection algorithm, which is a subfield of machine learning. The algorithm aims to improve the accuracy of device activity detection, which is a key concern in machine learning.
